description.ar: تحليق فوق دبي مع إطلالات بانورامية خلابة على أفق المدينة ووصول سلس إلى المرافق العالمية. يقع "ذا إيدن" في قلب مجمع "سُبحا سنترال"، ويقدم أسلوب حياة حضريًا راقيًا حيث تلتقي الطبيعة بأفق المدينة. يضم شققًا من غرفة نوم واحدة وغرفتي نوم، وقد تم تصميم كل وحدة سكنية لالتقاط إطلالات لا تنقطع على أفق دبي والمنصة ذات المناظر الطبيعية الخلابة أدناه، مما يجلب الهدوء والوضوح إلى الحياة اليومية. يتمتع "ذا إيدن" بموقع استراتيجي ضمن المخطط الرئيسي لـ "سُبحا سنترال"، ويوفر للسكان اتصالًا داخليًا سلسًا بالمجتمع الأوسع من خلال ردهات مصاعد متكاملة بذكاء. يربط هذا الوصول المباشر والمحمي من العوامل الجوية السكان بمركز تسوق متكامل، وسينما متعددة الشاشات، وصالة رياضية حديثة، وقاعة صلاة كبرى، وعيادة طبية، وسوبر ماركت، ومجموعة من المرافق الحيوية الأخرى المصممة لتعزيز الحياة اليومية براحة لا مثيل لها.

description.en: Sobha Aquamont ushers in a new era of refined coastal living in the heart of Downtown Umm Al Quwain. description.ar: مساكن شاطئ بريستين هي مزيج من الأناقة المعاصرة مع صفاء الحياة على شاطئ البحر. تقع هذه المجموعة الأخيرة من المساكن الشاطئية عند مدخل جزيرة شوبا سينيا، وتتصل بسلاسة عبر جسر بطول 1.7 كيلومتر بالبر الرئيسي. محاطة بإطلالات خلابة على بحر العرب بينما تحتضنها المساحات الخضراء المورقة، مساكن شاطئ بريستين على بعد دقائق من منتجعين فاخرين. اكتشف الحياة السهلة في مساكن البرج A الفاخرة المكونة من غرفة نوم واحدة وغرفتي نوم مفروشة بالكامل. تم تصميم كل مسكن بعناية لتوفير الراحة والأسلوب الذي لا مثيل له. ببساطة احزم حقائبك وادخل إلى حياة من الرقي والراحة المطلقة. استيقظ على إيقاع الأمواج، استرخِ على الشواطئ الذهبية، أو استمتع بإثارة مغامرات الشاطئ. سواء كنت تبحث عن الهدوء أو التواصل، تقدم هذه المساكن الشاطئية حياة حيث يلهم كل شروق شمس، ويشعر كل غروب وكأنه منزل.
description.en: Pristine Beach Residences is a blend of contemporary elegance with the serenity of beachfront living. Positioned at the very entrance of Sobha Siniya Island, this last cluster of Beach Residences is seamlessly connected via the 1.7 km bridge to the mainland. Surrounded by stunning views of the Arabian Sea while being cocooned in lush greenery, Pristine Beach Residences is minutes away from 2 luxurious resorts. Discover effortless living in Tower A's exquisite 1 & 2-bedroom fully furnished residences. Each residence is thoughtfully designed for comfort and unparalleled style. Simply pack your bags and step into a life of pure sophistication and ease. Wake up to the rhythm of the waves, unwind on golden shores, or embrace the thrill of beachside adventures. Whether seeking tranquillity or connection, these beachfront residences offer a life where every sunrise inspires, and every sunset feels like home.

description.ar: Discover Sobha Elwood, a luxurious villa community offering 4 to 6 bedroom villas surrounded by green living. Explore the variety of villas and modern amenities! Embodying the ethos of ‘The Canvas of Nature,’ Sobha Elwood epitomises luxury living. Each residence is a meticulously designed masterpiece, seamlessly integrating with the lush surroundings. The landscape (with dedicated 47% open space and parks) and parks here are inspired by the world's seven largest forests - from the Baobab to the Amazon rainforest - showcasing an array of trees from the most mystical and enchanting woodlands. This exclusive community features premium villas in 4, 5, and 6-bedroom configurations, each crafted to envelop residents in a tranquil and natural environment. Here, every breath is enriched with pristine air, and every step taken within this community draws you deeper into nature’s sublime embrace.

Together, they redefine urban sophistication and luxury living in Dubai.

Enjoy a 40-seater indoor movie theatre, relax in the sensory and zen gardens, and stay active with battle ropes, jumping blocks, and an aerobic zone. The community also features a dedicated gardening zone and spaces for chess and carrom, ensuring there's always something exciting to enrich your life.

The BBQ area, surrounded by lush greenery, invites you to relax and savour the simple joys of life—great food and an unforgettable dining experience under the open sky.

description.ar: Sobha Central is a landmark residential community rising on Sheikh Zayed Road, Dubai’s most iconic corridor. This architectural giant unites six sleek and elegant towers around lush, elevated parks, a tech-powered retail mall, along with dedicated office space, and curated lifestyle amenities. Designed as a vibrant neighborhood, it off­ers panoramic views, seamless connectivity, and a complete living experience —bringing together everything residents need at their doorstep, in one place. This is where it all connects.
description.en: Sobha Central is a landmark residential community rising on Sheikh Zayed Road, Dubai’s most iconic corridor. This architectural giant unites six sleek and elegant towers around lush, elevated parks, a tech-powered retail mall, along with dedicated office space, and curated lifestyle amenities. Designed as a vibrant neighborhood, it off­ers panoramic views, seamless connectivity, and a complete living experience —bringing together everything residents need at their doorstep, in one place. This is where it all connects.

Discover the epitome of connected living at Sobha Central, where luxurious residences offer unparalleled comfort and panoramic vistas. Every residence is designed to capture the essence of the city while delivering an elevated lifestyle infused with sophistication and serenity.

From premium office spaces, modern co-working areas & a business centre to fitness spaces and shaded green zones, everyday essentials flow seamlessly into one another — creating a community that feels alive, balanced, and built for the way people live and work. Every corner is purposefully placed — from the Grand Prayer Hall to the commercial gym, from boutique retail to the supermarket.

Sobha Central offers a plethora of vibrant dining options, from upscale restaurants to artisanal markets and boutique cafes blending international cuisine with local flavors all minutes away, just downstairs at the podium level and mall.

description.ar: Sobha One redefines luxury living in Dubai with an exclusive blend of modern sophistication and lush surroundings. Spreads over five interlinked towers and strategically located near Ras Al Khor Wildlife Sanctuary; it provides seamless access to Dubai’s prime destinations. The project boasts unique amenities, including infinity pools, tranquil parks, a world-class fitness centre, and concierge services, ensuring a refined lifestyle. Sobha One is where luxury, convenience, and green spaces come together in perfect harmony, offering an unparalleled living experience.

description.ar: The first beacon to rise within the Sobha Central constellation, The Horizon is perfectly positioned at the heart of the Bluewaters and JLT interchange. This architectural landmark offers breathtaking, unobstructed views across Dubai’s skyline from every 1- to 2-bedroom residence. With no surrounding towers within a 500-meter radius, residents enjoy uninterrupted vistas—from tranquil podium gardens to the boundless cityscape beyond. It’s elevated living where every window captures a sense of freedom.The Horizon also stands out for its seamless connectivity within the Sobha Central community. With interconnected lift lobbies linking to two adjacent towers, residents enjoy direct internal access to a world of amenities—including a shopping mall, cinema, gym, grand prayer hall, supermarket, and more.
